data.description: Don't Miss this Charming Hyattsville Home with an Open Floor Plan and Upgraded Features.   Welcome to your dream home! This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem is one of a kind and among the larger homes in the neighborhood. Major renovations were completed in October 2020. It is nestled on a picturesque street, offering a combination of modern comforts in a prime location.  Key Features:  - Spacious Open Floor Plan: As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright and open floor plan that effortlessly flows from room to room, perfect for modern living and entertaining.  - Oversized Owner's Bedroom: The generous owner's suite boasts an expansive walk-in closet, offering ample storage space for your wardrobe and personal items.  - Hardwood Floors: Gleaming hardwood floors run throughout the entire home, lending a touch of elegance and warmth to the interior.  - Newly Updated Kitchen: The kitchen has been thoughtfully updated with modern appliances, sleek countertops, and plenty of cabinet space to satisfy your culinary desires.  - Family Room with Deck Access: The large family room leads to a spacious composite two-tiered deck, perfect for enjoying outdoor living and entertaining. This deck overlooks a flat yard and is enclosed by a privacy fence, providing the ideal backdrop for relaxation and gatherings.  - Great Outdoor Living Space: With a flat yard and a privacy fence, the outdoor space is an oasis of tranquility where you can savor the Maryland seasons to the fullest.  - Centrally Located: This home is conveniently located, offering easy access to major roads, restaurants, and shopping centers within minutes. Plus, it's situated between the vibrant cities of Washington, D.C., and Baltimore, making your commute a breeze and providing access to all the amenities these cities offer. The proximity to BWI Airport ensures that you're never far from your next adventure.  Don't miss the opportunity to make 4115 Fairfax Street YOUR NEW HOME!   This house is an exceptional find in highly sought-after Landover Hills, offering a serene and comfortable lifestyle while being close to all the action. Schedule your visit today and envision the countless memories you'll create in this lovely abode.
